# Chrome Extension = circuit-breaker/dist

The **loaded extension** is `circuit-breaker/dist/`. Chrome loads this folder when you use "Load unpacked."

- **Always edit extension files in** `circuit-breaker/dist/`, not in `extension/` or other source folders.
- Key files: `manifest.json`, `background.js`, `content.js`, `content.css`, `popup.html`, `popup.js`, `popup.css`, and `icons/`.
- Changes in `circuit-breaker/dist/` are what the extension uses; reload the extension in `chrome://extensions` to see updates.
